00:05:34.900 --> 00:05:36.860
Every year, right here on Shadow Lane,

00:05:36.860 --> 00:05:39.140
little Elsie Soapristine launches a full-scale attack

00:05:39.140 --> 00:05:40.460
on yours truly.

00:05:40.460 --> 00:05:42.140
Here's a brief look at my personal combat

00:05:42.140 --> 00:05:43.580
record with little Elsie.

00:05:43.580 --> 00:05:46.900
But be warned, it's not for the faint of heart.

00:05:46.900 --> 00:05:48.860
Three years ago, little Elsie

00:05:48.860 --> 00:05:50.900
was in her arts and crafts stage,

00:05:50.900 --> 00:05:53.740
