00:06:12.480 --> 00:06:20.260
Figured out where she hid, I was too busy seeking shelter.

00:06:20.260 --> 00:06:22.260
Here was the last straw.

00:06:22.260 --> 00:06:24.660
I thought I could tame Elsie with my old Susie Baker

00:06:24.660 --> 00:06:25.780
